---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../../styles/content.css';
---
<BaseLayout title="Medical Equipment Planning for Healthcare Renovation Projects | Estrelis.ai" description="Plan equipment for hospital renovations and expansions. Inventory existing assets with iPad, identify reuse vs. replacement, and coordinate phased moves with AI-powered planning tools.">

  <section class="content-hero">
    <h1>Equipment Planning for Healthcare Renovations</h1>
    <p>Renovation projects add a unique layer of complexity: existing equipment must be inventoried, evaluated for reuse, and coordinated with new purchases across phased construction schedules.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>The Renovation Challenge</h2>
    <p>Unlike new construction, renovation projects start with existing equipment that must be assessed, cataloged, and either reused, relocated, or replaced. Teams must coordinate phased moves where some areas remain operational while others are under construction — all while maintaining patient care standards.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>How Estrelis Supports Renovation Planning</h2>
    <div class="content-grid">
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>iPad Field Inventory</h3>
        <p>Walk through existing facilities and capture equipment data with iPad — 360-degree panoramic photos, barcode scanning, and AI-powered asset identification. Build a complete picture of what exists before planning what's needed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Reuse vs. Replace Analysis</h3>
        <p>AI evaluates existing equipment against current standards, manufacturer lifecycle data, and project requirements to recommend reuse, relocation, or replacement for every item.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Phased Move Coordination</h3>
        <p>Plan equipment moves across construction phases. Track which items are being relocated, stored, or replaced — with clear visibility into what's happening in each phase.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="content-card">
        <h3>Budget Optimization</h3>
        <p>Maximize reuse of existing equipment to reduce project costs. Real-time budget tracking shows the impact of reuse decisions across departments and phases.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <h2>Common Renovation Scenarios</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Department expansions requiring additional equipment capacity</li>
      <li>Floor-by-floor renovations with phased equipment moves</li>
      <li>Technology upgrades replacing end-of-life imaging and OR equipment</li>
      <li>Seismic or code compliance renovations affecting equipment placement</li>
      <li>Mergers and acquisitions consolidating equipment across facilities</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Planning a healthcare renovation?</h2>
    <p>See how Estrelis handles the complexity of renovation equipment planning.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary btn-lg">Request a Demo</a>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
